message.body: How long are you gonna be at da party
I'm not sure those details haven't been worked out, maybe late? Why whats up
I don't think I can get there until midnight :(
Waaaat thats mad late, have you left maine yet?
I knowww. We are on the road but we are having a family dinner in long island with my grandma and uncles and stuff. It's a goodbye party thing. So I won't get back to the city till late
Hmm did you let diana know?
Yeah I did. She said its not too late if the party's still going. So you gotta keep it goin!
If anybody is under pressure to leave early, its joygill. But right after that is me. So i'll stay as long as i can!
Haha ok great thanks! I know people have their own curfews but I just wanna make sure I see as many people as I can!
I know i feel you, how was maine what'd you do?
It was fine, we were only there for a few days but we were able to go to the beach and play tennis and go into town. What have you been up to
Swag did you get to see claire and stuff? I've been fasting and praying mad hard. Pool was cool tho, whooped everyone, ate delicious mexican food and got stoned
Nahh claire lives in Vermont. Oh niiice that was Chelsea's birthday party right? Who was there
Me chelsea marianela and diana. We spent the whole time reminiscing and shit it was nice. Played an hour of pool alone tho :(
Aww that's nice. The only problem with going away this week was that everyone decided to plan shit at the end of summer. You had all summer guys, smh slakkin
Chill i can't change chelsea's birthday nigga it is what it is. Also this party was not my idea
Basically nothing's my fault and i'm perfect
Lmao yeah I wasn't blaming you for anything. We already planned our shit for earlier in the summer so we good
Save me some illicit substances!
Lmaoooo we got mad folks here dawg
Ugh pleeeaaazzzeeee
Hey what time are u leavin
EID MUBARAK!!!!
